        <h2 class="text_header">Description</h2>
        <p class="text_para">Linkage is a link aggregator web application. Linkage is intended to be a  a place where people can come and share links to funny videos, a link to a really good blog, or pretty much anything they find interesting on the internet. Users who signup can post their own links, edit their links, delete them, and even give a breif overview about why they are posting the link. Check out the code - <a href="https://github.com/Scotchard22/Linkage">Linkage</a></p>
